    "Looking ahead, the integration of these three technologies could be a prospect for future automotive E/E architectures, imparting higher levels of safety, reliability, and intelligence to future vehicles.",
    "Figure 7 outlines a developmental trajectory for networking technologies in automotive E/E architectures.",
    "Modeling and Simulation Technology for E/E ArchitecturesDesigning topologies and networking of E/E architectures may involve many different fields with high complexity.It is necessary to examine them by modeling and simulating before deployment.",
